        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "| Stage | Cron job | Schedule (KST) | 실행 경로 |\n|-------|----------|----------------|----------|\n| fetch | `recipe-ingestion-fetch` | **매일 11:00** | CLI → Pushgateway |\n| parse-submit | `recipe-ingestion-parse-submit` | **매일 11:30** (fallback) | Kafka consumer + CLI fallback |\n| parse-retrieve | `recipe-ingestion-parse-retrieve` | **매 5분** | CLI → Pushgateway |\n| persist | `recipe-ingestion-persist` | **매일 13:00** (fallback) | Kafka consumer + CLI fallback |\n| embed-submit | `recipe-ingestion-embed-submit` | **매일 14:30** (fallback) | Kafka consumer + CLI fallback |\n| embed-retrieve | `recipe-ingestion-embed-retrieve` | **매 5분** | CLI → Pushgateway |\n\n패널 시간 윈도: **5분 cron** → `[5m]`·`[30m]`, **일 1회 cron** → `[24h]`, 알림 정합 → `persist`·`parse-retrieve` fail `[30m]`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Job cadence reference",
      "type": "text",
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
